{
    "text": "bike + camping \ud83d\udeb4\u26fa  \ud83d\udc49 laundry remix in profile \ud83d\udc48  For this trip I\u2019m trying out the @restrap technical bikepacking system. They\u2019re so light! ~ excited to see how they cope outdoors.  At the centre of my cockpit sits a @mouscase + bike mount. Since it\u2019s group tour, I\u2019ll prolly be filming mostly with my phone on-the-go. The IntraLock system is superior to one that requires rotation\ud83d\udc4c buttery smooth.   \ud83d\udeb2 Specialized Diverge  \u26fa Big Agnes Copper Spur   I\u2019ve pinned a carousel on profile for a more detailed look at the individual items should you need it, like a checklist for your next trip perhaps \ud83e\udd17  Follow for more sick edits \ud83c\udfac\ud83d\udd25  #camping #editing #asmr #creative #cycling #bikepacking #sounddesign #filmmaking",
